Class SerializedMessage

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.communications.clientmessages.SerializedMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SerializedMessage extends Object implements Serializable
Enclose both communications and actions needed to be sent to the server in a single object, which is as well serializable.
